17:42.713 --> 17:45.064
<i>- I don't know.
- Okay.</i>

17:45.238 --> 17:48.850
<i>I'm on 100 feet.</i>

17:49.024 --> 17:52.332
<i>I'm gonna turn off my light.</i>

17:52.506 --> 17:54.508
<i>Can you turn on your light?</i>

17:57.380 --> 17:58.251
