18:38.073 --> 18:39.857
<i>What's your air?</i>

18:40.031 --> 18:41.990
<i>I'm 100 bar.</i>

18:42.164 --> 18:44.297
<i>Are you still at the wall?</i>

18:44.471 --> 18:49.345
<i>- Yeah, yeah, it's behind me.
- Okay, then-- [distorted]</i>

18:49.519 --> 18:51.869
<i>I can hardly hear you, it's...</i>

18:52.043 --> 18:53.958
<i>Just keep talking, okay?</i>

18:54.133 --> 18:57.179
