20:33.797 --> 20:35.146
<i>This isn't working.</i>

20:35.321 --> 20:36.278
<i>We need to get you
out of here!</i>

20:36.452 --> 20:38.149
<i>We will.</i>

20:38.324 --> 20:40.369
