01:02:21.476 --> 01:02:23.435
<i>I don't know!</i>

01:02:27.961 --> 01:02:29.833
<i>I don't know.</i>

01:02:32.574 --> 01:02:34.054
<i>Please go up.</i>

01:02:42.584 --> 01:02:44.325
<i>Go up, Drew.</i>

01:02:50.679 --> 01:02:54.422
<i>I'm going to put my BCD-jacket
under the rock and inflate it.</i>

01:02:54.596 --> 01:02:58.862
<i>This is it, okay? It's going
to work like an air cushion.</i>

01:02:59.036 --> 01:03:00.864
<i>This is going to work, okay?</i>

01:03:01.038 --> 01:03:02.561
<i>Okay, ready?</i>

01:03:13.180 --> 01:03:15.356
<i>- Yeah.
- Okay.</i>

01:03:15.530 --> 01:03:17.315
<i>Where is the inflator?</i>

01:03:20.405 --> 01:03:24.061
<i>It works. It's working!</i>

01:03:25.976 --> 01:03:30.197
<i>No, no, no! Fuck, the safety
